"{\"uid\": \"tnonline.com-20240806-olympics-report-diving-track-and-a-souvenir-photo\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Editor's note: Anna Laible of Lehighton is covering the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, with a team of fellow journalists from the University of North Carolina.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.8953022365030503, \"rank\": 0.04708849205333736, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}, {\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 41, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehighton_Area_School_District\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.430969175776034e-12, \"text\": \"Lehighton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehighton_Area_School_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehighton_Area_School_District\"}, {\"begin\": 82, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974684215, \"rank\": 2.531573061692007e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Editor's note\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 52, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow journalists\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"North Carolina\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is reporting regularly on her experience there for the Times News.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her experience\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"the Times News\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Day 7 Today started early with taking public transportation to the Aquatics Centre, where diving takes place.\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had a bit of an adventure trying to find the media entrance after walking a mile from the metro to get there, but we found it and were still able to see the 3m synchro men's springboard final.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"an adventure\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"the media entrance\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"a mile\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"the metro\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"the 3m synchro men's springboard final\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the final, I talked with Greg Duncan, who competed at UNC his freshman year, before taking the short trip across the bridge to Stade de France for track and field.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Duncan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Duncan\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Duncan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Duncan\"}, {\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina_Tar_Heels\", \"score\": 0.5752174609069608, \"rank\": 0.7328972932046967, \"text\": \"UNC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina_Tar_Heels\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina_Tar_Heels\"}, {\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the short trip\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridge\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was fun catching the end of the morning track and field session, and the media table overlooking the track field was my home for the next six hours working on different stories, and it wasn't a bad view!\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning track and field session\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"the media table\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the track field\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"my home\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the next six hours\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"different stories\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad view\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also fun to reconnect with my ESPN friend Coley Harvey, who I first met at March Madness and who has been on my podcast.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999999988838226, \"rank\": 9.196391152296496e-10, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coley_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999999695562569, \"rank\": 2.5912898577553682e-08, \"text\": \"Coley\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coley_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coley_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 976, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"score\": 0.7943706382716337, \"rank\": 0.2582968689773655, \"text\": \"Harvey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"March Madness\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"my podcast\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I caught some more track under the lights and then headed back to the hotel so I could grab dinner somewhere before midnight.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some more track\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"the lights\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"midnight\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Day 9 I enjoyed starting my day by meeting up with other UNC students at the Trocadero and having a group lunch for the first time in the last week.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina_Tar_Heels\", \"score\": 0.5752174609069608, \"rank\": 0.7328972932046967, \"text\": \"UNC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina_Tar_Heels\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina_Tar_Heels\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my day\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"a group lunch\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the last week\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After that, we headed to the hospitality suite to interview Dean Linke, who I have had on my podcast, and his wife, Leah, and we had a great conversation with both of them.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9997553507374016, \"rank\": 0.00024433677018402956, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah_Patterson-Baker\", \"score\": 0.9999999996528004, \"rank\": 2.1200067078557206e-10, \"text\": \"Leah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah_Patterson-Baker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah_Patterson-Baker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hospitality suite\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"my podcast\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"a great conversation\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After that, we were able to tour around the amazing building with all the Olympic medals from every Olympics, the Olympic torch, Olympic flag, and even the Olympic mascot.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the amazing building\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"all the Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"every Olympics\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We also were able to take pictures with the Olympic rings, which I have always wanted to do!\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pictures\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then we grabbed some food and desserts and watched gymnastics on a big screen outside before I headed out to go to track and field.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some food\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"desserts\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"a big screen\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After I covered a South Carolina athlete in the prelims, I had a front-row seat to watch what was, in my opinion, the most exciting men's 100m final of all time.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1919, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Gamecocks\", \"score\": 0.4461192688953794, \"rank\": 0.7391205960663039, \"text\": \"South Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Gamecocks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Gamecocks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prelims\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"a front-row seat\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA's Noah Lyles won by 0.005, the first American to win the race in 20 years.\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6156511667167359, \"rank\": 0.6155878880778981, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2075, \"end\": 2085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999684753919239, \"rank\": 1.3917746070267854e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such a great day and I can not wait to see gymnastics one final time tomorrow!\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Such a great day\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2202}, {\"ngram\": \"one final time\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2217}]}]}"